lands and fight to survive.<br>Some enemies drop rare resource materials that you will need to <br>upgrade new towers, weapons, &amp; armor.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/f6c3b78719d7d4b2de235dd5792bac34.poster.avif?t=1708179500\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/f6c3b78719d7d4b2de235dd5792bac34.webm?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/f6c3b78719d7d4b2de235dd5792bac34.mp4?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/506a0fef83e008d244ebefcdf2188fbb.poster.avif?t=1708179500\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/506a0fef83e008d244ebefcdf2188fbb.webm?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/506a0fef83e008d244ebefcdf2188fbb.mp4?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/40fe224e7abd961bcafb03e9ddc9c1a6.poster.avif?t=1708179500\" width=618 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/40fe224e7abd961bcafb03e9ddc9c1a6.webm?t=1708179500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902640/extras/40fe224e7abd961bcafb03e9ddc9c1a6.mp4?t=1708179500\"